      <title>特朗普在环球电视网谈论斯普林菲尔德宠物、伊隆·马斯克</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/springfield-pets-musk-s-role-harris-traits-trump-on-univision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在联合电视网与拉丁裔选民举行的市政厅会议上，前总统唐纳德·特朗普被问及他的移民言论、经济问题和他一届白宫任期内的记录，拉丁裔选民群体将决定他在关键战场州的选举命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/springfield-pets-musk-s-role-harris-traits-trump-on-univision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 19:42:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德呼吁欧洲将挑战作为变革的动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/lagarde-calls-on-europe-to-use-challenges-as-impetus-for-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长拉加德表示，欧洲应利用日益碎片化的世界秩序和地缘政治冲突带来的挑战，作为加强国内市场基础的机遇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/lagarde-calls-on-europe-to-use-challenges-as-impetus-for-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 18:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利通过法案，将境外代孕定为犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/italy-passes-bill-to-criminalize-surrogacy-carried-out-abroad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利议会通过了一项法案，将对通过代孕在国外生孩子的父母判处监禁——即使该过程是合法进行的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/italy-passes-bill-to-criminalize-surrogacy-carried-out-abroad</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 18:17:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多描述与莫迪进行静默外交的失败尝试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/trudeau-describes-failed-efforts-at-quiet-diplomacy-with-modi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，在印度政府长期试图通过外交手段解决此事但遭到印度官员拒绝后，他才公开提出涉及印度政府的谋杀指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/trudeau-describes-failed-efforts-at-quiet-diplomacy-with-modi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 18:11:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德鲁肯米勒称市场“非常确信”特朗普将获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/druckenmiller-says-market-is-very-convinced-trump-will-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁投资者斯坦·德鲁肯米勒 (Stan Druckenmiller) 表示，在下个月的美国总统大选之前，市场已经消化了唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 获胜的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/druckenmiller-says-market-is-very-convinced-trump-will-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 17:52:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰总统图斯克视清洁能源为经济新增长引擎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/poland-s-tusk-sees-clean-energy-as-new-growth-engine-for-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·塔斯克表示，向清洁能源转型将推动波兰未来经济增长，这表明波兰政府希望认真考虑逐步摆脱对煤炭的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/poland-s-tusk-sees-clean-energy-as-new-growth-engine-for-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 17:47:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦肯锡将向美国司法部阿片类药物调查支付至少 5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/mckinsey-poised-to-pay-at-least-500-million-in-doj-opioid-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，麦肯锡公司即将与美国检察官达成协议，将支付至少 5 亿美元，以解决联邦对其过去帮助阿片类药物制造商提高销量的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/mckinsey-poised-to-pay-at-least-500-million-in-doj-opioid-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 17:41:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RTX 将支付超过 5 亿美元以解决美国刑事调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/rtx-to-pay-290-million-to-settle-us-criminal-corruption-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[RTX 公司同意支付超过 5 亿美元，以解决与其试图在卡塔尔赢得业务以及该公司的采购行为有关的多项联邦刑事调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/rtx-to-pay-290-million-to-settle-us-criminal-corruption-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 15:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冲突升级，以色列加强对黎巴嫩的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/israel-steps-up-air-strikes-in-lebanon-as-war-in-north-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列加强了对黎巴嫩的空袭，并称该国南部真主党的一名高级指挥官被杀，这是以色列与伊朗支持的激进组织之间冲突的最新升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/israel-steps-up-air-strikes-in-lebanon-as-war-in-north-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 15:32:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基在欧洲之行后向议员们宣传胜利计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/zelenskiy-presents-victory-plan-to-lawmakers-after-europe-tour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基向议员们介绍了他的“胜利计划”，概述了他结束俄罗斯入侵的愿景，并重申该国不能接受冻结冲突或用领土换取和平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/zelenskiy-presents-victory-plan-to-lawmakers-after-europe-tour</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 09:57:30 GMT</pubDate>
